# Design generic CI/CD webhook interface

Design abstraction layer for handling webhooks from various CI/CD platforms.

## Requirements

- [ ] Design `PagServer.Integrations.CiCd.WebhookAdapter` behaviour
- [ ] Define standard webhook event interface:
  - [ ] Build/pipeline ID
  - [ ] Status (pending, running, success, failure)
  - [ ] Timestamp information
  - [ ] URL/log references
  - [ ] Associated repository/project info
- [ ] Document platform-specific implementations:
  - [ ] CircleCI adapter mapping
  - [ ] Jenkins adapter mapping
  - [ ] Drone adapter mapping
- [ ] Design event routing based on webhook type
- [ ] Document signature verification patterns
- [ ] Create adapter integration tests

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Behaviour module defined with required callbacks
- [ ] Standard event struct supports all platform variations
- [ ] Platform mappings clearly documented
- [ ] Routing logic handles different event schemas
- [ ] Example implementations for each platform
- [ ] Integration tests verify adapter pattern works
- [ ] `mix test` passes for all tests
- [ ] `mix lint` passes without warnings


